<item>
            <title>[LU-9175] interop: sanity test_102n: before and after xattrs of &apos;/mnt/lustre/f102n.sanity.1&apos; differ</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-9175</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Bob Glossman &amp;lt;bob.glossman@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/e2cdcd2e-ff93-11e6-aa1f-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/e2cdcd2e-ff93-11e6-aa1f-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_102n failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;before and after xattrs of &apos;/mnt/lustre/f102n.sanity.1&apos; differ
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This looks a lot like a repeat of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8129&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_102n: before and after xattrs of &amp;#39;/mnt/lustre/f102n.sanity.1&amp;#39; differ &quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-8129&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-8129&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, but this was seen on b2_8_fe long after the fix from that ticket was landed; &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/20112&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/20112&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 102n&lt;/p&gt;</description>
